  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "While the proposed method demonstrates notable improvements in NER performance, the study acknowledges some limitations.",
    "First, the reliance on distant supervision and Wikipedia categories may introduce noise into the weakly labeled data, potentially affecting accuracy.",
    "Second, the model's adaptability to more informal or domain-specific texts, such as social media posts, remains unexplored.",
    "Future research could focus on refining the weak-labeling process to reduce noise and exploring the model's applicability to other forms of contemporary text beyond news articles and encyclopedic content.",
    "Moreover, investigating how this approach can be extended to languages other than English could further enhance its utility in multilingual contexts (Kim et al., 2021)."
  ],
